:: Dubai-ification of the world_brief (2include) DB {"position":"8105,7705"}
A world that relies principally on adaptation to climate change will trend towards a situation where the poor cannot survive and the rich create a technology-dominated life support system with water from desalination plants (where deserts are spreading), food is grown and people live under air conditioned domes or they live in the new green areas of Antarctica and the Arctic Circle - in a process that could be thought of as the Dubai-ification of the world[[|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dubai]].